PORTFOLIO

Shadow Flips

Shadow Flips is an extension on twitch, which allow users to exchange bits for points, then use those points to flip the screen (Shadow Flip), turn it off (Shadow Kick), or play sound effects. There is also a bot that runs on your PC which reads the inputs from the extension, and does the physical flips, and kicks, and sounds. The bot also interacts with OBS Studio or Streamlabs OBS to simulate the flips/kicks so the viewers can see it too!

https://shadowflips.com

Chat Matrix

Stream Overlay that will display the latest chat messages in a Matrix Style display.

https://chat-matrix.ttvtools.com/?channel=CHANNELNAME

OneDoesNotSimp.ly

A meme generator that is based on the Lord of the Rings meme One Does Not Simply Walk Into Mordor

https://onedoesnotsimp.ly
